field.name: PROOF_OF_APPROVAL_DESC
field.value: "Indicates that the signer has approved the content of the signed data object"

field.name: PROOF_OF_CREATION_DESC
field.value: "Indicates that the signer has created the signed data object (but not necessarily approved, nor sent it)"

field.name: PROOF_OF_DELIVERY_DESC
field.value: "Indicates that the TSP providing that indication has delivered a signed data object in a local store accessible to the recipient of the signed data object"

field.name: PROOF_OF_ORIGIN_DESC
field.value: "Indicates that the signer recognizes to have created, approved and sent the signed data object"

field.name: PROOF_OF_RECEIPT_DESC
field.value: "Indicates that signer recognizes to have received the content of the signed data object"

field.name: PROOF_OF_SENDER_DESC
field.value: "Indicates that the entity providing that indication has sent the signed data object (but not necessarily created it)"
